                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">
                  Video call sessions
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Video call therapy sessions.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="faq" class="faq-section py-20 bg-gray-50">
          <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">
                Frequently Asked Questions
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Find answers to common questions about TherapEase and our
                services.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-container max-w-4xl mx-auto">
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  What is TherapEase?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  TherapEase is an online platform connecting individuals with
                  licensed therapists for personalized therapy sessions. We aim
                  to make mental health care accessible, flexible, and reliable.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  How does online therapy work?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  Online therapy at TherapEase allows you to connect with
                  certified therapists via video, voice, or text sessions. After
                  completing a quick screening, you'll be matched with a
                  therapist based on your specific needs.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  What types of therapy do you offer?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  We offer individual therapy, child therapy, couple therapy,
                  and specialized services like teen or relationship counseling.
                  Each therapy session is tailored to your unique goals.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  Are my conversations private and secure?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  Absolutely. Your privacy is our priority. We use advanced
