                  secure and confidential.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  How do I pay for therapy sessions?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  Payments are processed online through secure gateways. You can
                  pay via debit/credit cards or other supported methods.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  Can I change my therapist if I'm not satisfied?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  Yes, you can request a change at any time. We believe in
                  finding the right match for effective therapy, so we make this
                  process simple and straightforward.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 cursor-pointer">
                  How often should I schedule therapy sessions?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                  This varies based on individual needs. Most clients begin with
